### Test Readwise Connection
POST http://localhost:3000/api/readwise/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "token"
}

### Test Mem Connection
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mem/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "token"
}

### Fetch Readwise Highlights (Full Sync)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/readwise/fetch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "token"
}

### Fetch Readwise Highlights (Date Range)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/readwise/fetch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "token",
  "dateRange": {
    "start": "2024-01-01",
    "end": "2024-12-31"
  }
}

### Create Single Note in Mem
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mem/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "your_mem_api_key_here",
  "note": {
    "content": "# Test Note\n\nThis is a test note from API",
    "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  }
}

### Validate Highlights
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sync/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "highlights": [],
  "books": []
}

### Execute Sync
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sync/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "token",
  "validationSummary": {
    "results": []
  },
  "books": []
}

### Schedule Sync
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sync/schedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test-user-123",
  "frequency": "daily",
  "enabled": true
}

### Get Schedule
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sync/schedule?userId=test-user-123

### Save Credentials
POST http://localhost:3000/api/storage/save-credentials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test-user-123",
  "credentials": {
    "readwiseToken": "token",
    "memApiKey": "key"
  }
}

### Get Credentials
GET http://localhost:3000/api/storage/get-credentials?userId=test-user-123
